  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Retrospectively have access to MR images of patients to develop software that:

        1. segment images

        2. convert MR values to electron density and then

        3. entered into a dose calculation system

      The project involves software development of data that is already available. No intervention
      is made at this point.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
